{"tid":837761,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[AN/I] ブレイドスマッシュ blade-smash 四人大亂鬥 27/9 11am開波 開定先","createTime":"2018-09-26T15:18:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-28T02:58:21.000Z","uid":183798,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"09c39ee74c59142ed70e6b7b66b7058fa1e48415","tid":837761,"uid":183798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T15:18:22.000Z","msg":"ブレイドスマッシュ blade-smash<br />\n<br />\n配信日\t2018年9月27日<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">中午十二點（日本時間）<br />\n早上十一點（香港時間）</span><br />\n会社\tgumi<br />\n<br />\n4人大亂鬥 格鬥向<br />\n<br />\nBy飛鼠 新game終於要出現<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=kM034a6FHQk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DkM034a6FHQk&d=bXVSS1kgvuXGrx8aV44%2B0b%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=40b66a5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=kM034a6FHQk</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇畫面打擊感一流 人設唔錯<br />\n希望競技成份高啲 平衡少少<br />\n同埋技術含量多少少 唔會咁易悶 ～<br />\n<br />\n對呢隻game充滿期待 呢排無咩game提起興趣"},{"pid":"58da27f953f41674d9a4e46dc442527e2e4fb235","tid":837761,"uid":29093,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T15:20:16.000Z","msg":"又係一年貨仔    賺夠就摺埋  嗰啲"},{"pid":"d2a6d41b9521ec062613ea88f6a5638842b48089","tid":837761,"uid":183798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58da27f953f41674d9a4e46dc442527e2e4fb235","tid":837761,"uid":29093,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T15:20:16.000Z","msg":"又係一年貨仔    賺夠就摺埋  嗰啲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T15:23:29.000Z","msg":"唉呢排已經悶到癲 無咩手機game好玩<br />\n<br />\n玩開啲好快一場、有競技成份、人設特效都ok既game <br />\n<br />\n卡牌有sv又執柒左 玩brawlstar又玩兩玩好悶<br />\n爐石好多年前棄左 遊戲王又係 <br />\n<br />\n希望呢隻玩耐啲"},{"pid":"3487b75c5602c3d2c1e38d386adc0a381f80538b","tid":837761,"uid":183798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T15:28:02.000Z","msg":"推下先 有冇人留意到新驚"},{"pid":"1e5d1491ac2f8d0d7961faec06a7c879db5a2612","tid":837761,"uid":84360,"like":0,"d